### 可视化概览
GET http://localhost:5000/visualization/overview
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant_id}}

### 可视化流程列表
GET http://localhost:5000/visualization/processes?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant_id}}

### 可视化实例列表
GET http://localhost:5000/visualization/instances?pageIndex=1&pageSize=10
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant_id}}

### 校验流程定义
POST http://localhost:5000/visualization/processes/validate
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "definitionJson": "{ \"nodes\": [], \"edges\": [] }"
}

### 发布流程定义
POST http://localhost:5000/visualization/processes/publish
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
X-Tenant-Id: {{tenant_id}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "processId": "sample-flow",
  "version": 1,
  "note": "demo publish"
}
